On page load:
    Read TLS info
        store aside certificate (if any) and choose appropriate icon.
    Check URI scheme,
        Mark odysseus:, file:, about:, (& eventually IPFS) as "incognito".
insecure_content_detected:
    use less secure icon.

On click:
    Iterate over certificate chain,
        Add a button containing a 2wide x 3tall grid with the GCR parsed info
        On button click:
            Serialize text to string
            Open in new tab
            Add tab to dynamic listbox
            Focus new tab.
